title: Woo Joo-young
text:
Woo Joo-Young (<a href="Hangul">Hangul</a>: 우주영; born 18 January 1981) is a retired <a href="South%20Korea">South Korean</a> <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> player.
He participated in the <a href="Football%20at%20the%202009%20East%20Asian%20Games">2009 East Asian Games</a> as a member of <a href="South%20Korea">South Korea</a>.
